ect them to on-campus resources, conduct educational outreach activities, and assist the functions of the Student Assistance area in the Office of the Dean of Students. Heading link xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"? Copy link How can I contribute? A gift can be made online Assistance Back to main content Academic Concerns Academic Resources Academic Grievances Withdrawal Emergencies and Absences Health & Personal Concerns Hospitalization & Emergencies Mental Health Victims of Crime and Safety Concerns Basic Needs Insecurity Financial Concerns Cannabis: Know the Facts Campus Life Faculty & Staff Resources The Student Response Team Behavioral Response Intervention Team U & I Care Meet Our Partners Care Facts News & Events U & I Care Fund U & I Care Plan University of Illinois Chicago DOS Offices Career Services Student Employment Counseling Center Wellness Center For Employees SA Human Resources SA Technology GoTime Log-in The Pulse Safety UIC Police Office of Access & Equity Contact-US Giving Social Media Accounts xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"? Facebook xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"? Twitter xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"? Instagram xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"? YouTube Contact 1200 West Harrison St., 3030 SSB Chicago, IL 60607 Phone: (312) 996-4857 dos@uic.edu UIC.edu links UIC.edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Safe Mobile App UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Powered by Red 3.0.51 | Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana-Champaign Springfield</TEXT>